description:
Is everyone just as confused as we are in regards to Kim Kardashian and Pete Davidson dating? This week Aleena and Madi dive deep into Pete's dating history, Kim's past relationship with Kayne, and potential theories on why this unlikely pair maybe exactly what each of them needs (trust me, we go through the psychology behind rebounding and the science of attraction to try and figure this one out). Spoiler alert: There's a lot to unpack this week so join us for some more educational basic b***h fun :)
